thread.title: dan abicidan

author: dan abicidan
title: dan abicidan
text: Great supplier! That's all I can say. I've been buying from MyPrinterShop for like 3 years now, and they are supplying the toner for all our printers. We get it super quickly, and it's always top notch quality. We started off by buying OEM, but then their rep suggested we try compatible cartidges to save money. We tried it out, and quality was just as great, and now it's all we order!
